@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
actor "Customer" as C
participant "Admin" as A
control "Delivery Service" as DS
participant "Payment Gateway" as PG
actor "Seller" as S
A ->> C : Manage Inventory
activate C
C --> A : ACK
deactivate C
note over C : processing manage inventory
A -> S : Make Payment
DS ->> S : Write Review
S ->> DS : Checkout
activate DS
DS --> S : ACK
deactivate DS
PG -> DS : Apply Coupon
PG ->> DS : Browse Products
note over DS : processing browse products
C ->> A : Add To Cart
@enduml